  "keyFeatures": [
    "Lightweight JavaScript runtime built in C",
    "Full ES6+ support with async/await and modules",
    "Built-in package manager compatible with npm registry",
    "HTTP/HTTPS server with routing support",
    "Foreign Function Interface (FFI) for C libraries",
    "Embeddable as a C library (libant)",
    "Cross-platform (Linux, macOS, Windows)",
    "REPL with interactive debugging",
    "Built-in crypto, file system, and networking APIs",
    "Worker threads and shared memory support"
